            <h1>
              时空框架变迁及电脑网络对语言行为的形塑
            </h1>
            <h2>
              Changes of Space-time Dimension and Cyberspace's Impact on Language and Behavior
            </h2>
            <div id="ctl00_LeftContentPlaceHolder_periodical">
              <p id="fulltext" style="visibility:visible">
                <a href="/Service/File/view/时空框架变迁及电脑网络对语言行为的形塑.aspx?ID=Periodical_xsjl200311029" class="seeft">
                </a>
                <a href="/Service/File/download/Periodical_xsjl200311029.aspx" class="downloadft">
                </a>
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>
                <a href="/Service/ResourcesExport/ResourcesExport.aspx?rs=Periodical_xsjl200311029" class="export">
                </a>
              </p>
            </div>
            <div id="downloadpdf">
              <a href="/Service/Readerdownload.aspx">
                下载PDF阅读器
              </a>
